{"tid":622933,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傑志U20前球員向進豪販毒認罪判囚14年","createTime":"2018-04-09T14:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T16:44:58.000Z","uid":11496,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"006786858d529faae3c0ef60ea8eafcb051665cf","tid":622933,"uid":11496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記得以前舊登有人爆佢食女d料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/221333_7d80adf9f6d595ec643e3c3206e89944.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F221333_7d80adf9f6d595ec643e3c3206e89944.png&h=c4cf266f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾代表傑志U20組別的球員向進豪，2014年參與5人足球賽贏得過冠軍，並同時榮膺最有價值球員（MVP），惟去年5月卻在藍田公屋住所及樓下販運826克可卡因被捕，涉案毒品市值更高達97萬，他今（9日）於高等法院承認兩項販毒罪，法官根據涉案毒品重量，把判刑起點定為21年，考慮被告認罪等求情因素獲減刑，但仍須入獄14年。辯方求情時指向進豪因欠下6萬賭債，加上難抵2萬報酬的利誘下犯案。<br />\n<br />\n被告向進豪（21歲）報稱任職保安員，過往沒案底的，他承認去年5月1日在藍田邨藍蔚樓住處及地下販運822克及4.8克可卡因。<br />\n<br />\n網上賭博欠下6萬賭債<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，被告父母於被告10歲時離異，並由母親撫養，亦未有再見親父。具中五學歷的被告於16歲開始投身職場，惟因網上賭博而欠下6萬賭債，後來在網吧認識一個名叫「阿文」的人，「阿文」知他財困，便問他想不想賺快錢，被告為得到2萬報酬而犯下本案。辯方又指，被告於本案角色只是送遞毒品，非案中主腦，其母校校長及老師亦為他撰寫求情信，信中指被告是個好學生，精於足球，並對學校足球隊有巨大貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n認部份毒品自用<br />\n<br />\n案情指，去年5月1日，被告於住所樓下被搜出有822克可卡因，其後再於他房間搜出4.8克可卡因，警誡下承認犯案，又指部份可卡因為自用，其餘是用以包裝。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCCC436/2017<br />\n<br />\nSource: 香港01<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/176140/傑志u20前球員向進豪欠賭債下販毒-認罪判囚14年?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F176140%2F%E5%82%91%E5%BF%97u20%E5%89%8D%E7%90%83%E5%93%A1%E5%90%91%E9%80%B2%E8%B1%AA%E6%AC%A0%E8%B3%AD%E5%82%B5%E4%B8%8B%E8%B2%A9%E6%AF%92-%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A14%E5%B9%B4%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=4dxi23YR79Ul%2FUsxr1StjgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=9d727b2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/176140/傑志u20前球員向進豪欠賭債下販毒-認罪判囚14年?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a>"},{"pid":"420b30f9edf824ffac15de68180fbf1f273991f2","tid":622933,"uid":11073,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"人生就係咁完撚左<br />\nBtw真係狗公"},{"pid":"08028589f8e9b275fc91656a56741a477bfe6862","tid":622933,"uid":8990,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T19:47:10.000Z","msg":"狗公豪都有今日"},{"pid":"970fb277b68753d58865cc8223c6f33cf692b97e","tid":622933,"uid":11496,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"08028589f8e9b275fc91656a56741a477bfe6862","tid":622933,"uid":8990,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T19:47:10.000Z","msg":"狗公豪都有今日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T23:41:56.000Z","msg":"想知更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前都有睇過話咩借醉呃人上屋企<br />\n唔比扑就發脾氣"},{"pid":"e405dbba4006f4ae7f68e3a13f7fa2ea70201ad7","tid":622933,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T23:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f747fb75a234b6ac07002f152e1bc59fb39d3624","tid":622933,"uid":28758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T23:46:14.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"15350b8309684e17f9f2b2f4e16cd958badc54e7","tid":622933,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T00:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" cl